title: 820-02098 after water damage 5v 0a no Magsafe light.

Check first U8100 and U7700 LDOs; pages 41 & 37.

title: 820-02098 after water damage 5v 0a no Magsafe light.
message:
Do you mean PP1V8_AON?
In such case, U8100 is the first suspect.
Can also have bad solders underneath; try reballing it first.
